  "note": "284B-param MoE (13B activated), 1M context. Smaller sibling of DeepSeek-V4-Pro sharing the same hybrid compressed attention: Heavily Compressed Attention (HCA, kv_compression_ratio 128, local sliding window 128) and Compressed Sparse Attention (CSA, kv_compression_ratio 4 + DSA indexer top-k 512) interleaved per the config's compress_ratios = [0, 0, 4, 128, 4, 128, ...] where 0 = uncompressed full attention. The first two layers and the final layer run full attention; the remaining layers alternate HCA/CSA. All layers are MLA with a low-rank output projection (o_lora_rank 1024, o_groups 8). First 3 layers dense, remaining 40 MoE (256 routed experts, 6 active, 1 shared). The MLA latent dims (kv_lora_rank, qk_nope_head_dim, v_head_dim) and the dense FFN intermediate_size are reconstructed from the DeepSeek-V3.2/V4-Pro lineage as the public config truncates them; mHC hyper-connections (hc_mult 4) are a residual-path feature with negligible roofline impact and are not separately modelled.",
